query:
SELECT
  COUNT(distinct token) as record_count,
  NOW() as present_time
FROM
(
  SELECT token
  FROM generic_inference_jobs
  WHERE status = "started"
  AND created_at > (CURDATE() - INTERVAL 5 MINUTE)
UNION
  SELECT token
  FROM generic_inference_jobs
  WHERE status IN ("pending", "attempt_failed")
) as t
